409
00:37:47,000 --> 00:37:49,000
Look at his chest.

410
00:37:56,390 --> 00:37:57,680
The Blood Sect.

411
00:37:59,300 --> 00:38:03,300
At the time, there were a lot of Blood Sect disciples
that came and caused trouble.

412
00:38:03,300 --> 00:38:06,000
My men kept following them.

413
00:38:06,000 --> 00:38:09,900
Finally, in a cave where they were hiding,
my men also found Mi Tengshan.

414
00:38:09,900 --> 00:38:12,200
